phdl.designer
Class PHDLInstance

java.lang.Object
  phdl.designer.PHDLInstance

public class PHDLInstance
extends java.lang.Object

A class that models a device instance on a PCB. A device instance that contains an instance name, the name of the device it is modeled after

Version:
0.1
Author:
Richard Black and Brad Riching
